  <brief_title>May Preoperative Waist to Height Ratio Predict Postoperative Weight Loss in Bariatric Patients?</brief_title>
  <official_title>May Preoperative Waist to Height Ratio Predict Postoperative Weight Loss in Bariatric Patients?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
